# Local env files must never ship — Vercel injects env vars from the dashboard.
# (vercel deploy uploads the working dir and does NOT honor .gitignore, so a
# leaked .env AUTH_URL=http://localhost:3000 was overriding the real host and
# breaking the /admin auth cookie. Keep these out of the deployment.)
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.development.local
.env.production.local
.env*.local
